candidates.title: Bump syntect from 4.1.1 to 4.2.0

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

candidates.body:
Bumps [syntect](https://github.com/trishume/syntect) from 4.1.1 to 4.2.0.
Release notes

Sourced from syntect's releases.

New onig and plist versions

  • Updates to new versions of onig and plist. The new onig version doesn't require bindgen thus making compilation easier. #293
Changelog

Sourced from syntect's changelog.

Version 4.2.0 (2020-04-20)

  • Updates to new versions of onig and plist. The new onig version doesn't require bindgen thus making compilation easier. #293
Commits
  • b2360ea Changelog for v4.2.0
  • 1c7e27a Merge pull request #293 from Keats/master
  • 2685482 Update dependencies
  • 064ae75 Merge pull request #290 from out-of-cheese-error/master
  • 39cb3c9 Add the-way to "Projects using Syntect"
  • See full diff in compare view
